00:06:11.840 --> 00:06:17.370
JAWS and NVDA,
uh which I regularly use now as part of my

00:06:17.370 --> 00:06:22.560
job and day-to-day activities on the computer.

00:06:22.560 --> 00:06:27.699
So even as a person with a power screen reader
user, like I've been using for 15 years the

00:06:27.699 --> 00:06:33.690
screen reader, even for me when I initially
uh started with Gutenberg, it needs a lot

00:06:33.690 --> 00:06:37.580
of learning curve,
because there are no tutorials on how to use

00:06:37.580 --> 00:06:45.690
Gutenberg with a screen reader. So I'll be
